## File Structure Conventions

### Feature Module
```
feature/myfeature/
├── build.gradle.kts           # Module dependencies
├── src/main/java/.../myfeature/
│   ├── MyFeatureActivity.kt    # Entry point
│   ├── MyFeatureScreen.kt      # State + lifecycle
│   ├── MyFeatureViewModel.kt   # Logic & state
│   ├── di/
│   │   └── MyFeatureModule.kt  # Koin bindings
│   ├── navigator/
│   │   └── MyFeatureNavigatorImpl.kt  # Cross-feature nav
│   ├── ui/
│   │   ├── MyFeatureView.kt    # Stateless views
│   │   ├── MyFeatureContent.kt # Content sections
│   │   ├── MyFeatureCard.kt    # Reusable components
│   │   └── MyFeaturePreview.kt # Preview composables
│   ├── uimodel/
│   │   └── MyFeatureUI.kt      # UI-only data models
│   └── (no imports from :shared:data, :shared:api, :shared:database)
└── src/test/java/...
    └── MyFeatureViewModelTest.kt
```

### Data Layer
```
shared/data/
├── myentity/
│   └── MyRepositoryImpl.kt       # Implements domain interface (features never import this)

shared/api/
├── myentity/
│   └── MyRequestImpl.kt          # Remote calls (e.g. Ktor)
└── core/remote/
    └── MyApiService.kt          # Typed HTTP facade

shared/database/   # KMP module `:shared:database` — `src/commonMain/kotlin/...`
├── myentity/
│   ├── MyEntityDao.kt           # Room DAO
│   ├── MyEntityBase.kt          # Room entity
│   └── MyDataStoreImpl.kt       # Local persistence
```

