## Screen Composition Pattern

Every feature screen has 2 layers:

```
Activity
  ↓
Screen (Container Composable)
  ├─ collectAsState() from ViewModel
  ├─ collectLatest() for errors/events
  ├─ DisposableEffect() for lifecycle
  └─ Delegates to View
        ↓
        View (Stateless Composable)
        ├─ Pure UI rendering
        ├─ No state collection
        └─ All data via parameters
```

### Screen Responsibilities:
- Inject ViewModel via `koinViewModel()`
- Collect `StateFlow` → `State`
- Observe lifecycle events (ON_START to reload)
- Show error snackbars
- Delegate rendering to View

### View Responsibilities:
- Pure UI rendering
- NO side effects
- NO state collection
- Accept all data & callbacks as parameters
- Include `@Preview` composables

