## Data Flow: From Repository to UI

```
ViewModel
  ↓
Repository.getItems()  [interface]
  ↓
RepositoryImpl.getItems()  [implementation]
  ├─ requests to API Module
  │   └─ MyRequestImpl → Retrofit → ApiService → HTTP call
  │
  └─ queries local storage
      └─ MyDataStoreImpl → DAO → Room database
  ↓
combine(local, remote)  [if both needed]
  ↓
Flow<List<Entity>>  [domain model]
  ↓
ViewModel.viewModelScope.collect()
  ↓
_uiState.update { Data(items.mapToUI()) }  [UI model]
  ↓
Screen.collectAsState()
  ↓
View renders UI model
```

