## Testing Strategy

### What to Test

| Layer | What | How |
|-------|------|-----|
| **ViewModel** | State transitions, error handling | Mockito + Turbine |
| **Repository** | Data merging, error cases | Mockito + Flow.test() |
| **API** | Serialization, error mapping | Unit tests |
| **Database** | Query correctness | In-memory Room |
| **Compose** | Visual rendering, interaction | Previews + Espresso |

### Test Pattern (Given/When/Then)
```kotlin
@Test
fun `feature displays items when loaded`() = runTest {
    // Given: mock data is available
    coEvery { repository.getItems() } returns flow { emit(mockItems) }
    
    // When: ViewModel starts
    viewModel.start()
    
    // Then: UI state contains items
    viewModel.uiState.test {
        assert(awaitItem() is Loading)
        assert(awaitItem() is Data)
    }
}
```

