## Koin Dependency Injection

### Module Registration

**In feature module** (`di/MyFeatureModule.kt`):
```kotlin
val myFeatureModule = module {
    viewModelOf(::MyFeatureViewModel)
    single<MyFeatureNavigator> { MyFeatureNavigatorImpl(get()) }
}
```

**`commonMain` Koin modules** (`shared/di/.../SharedKoinArchiModules.kt`) define `apiModule` / `dataModule`; **Android edge** (`app/.../di/DatabaseModule.kt`) defines `databaseModule` (Room + DataStores). **`appCoreArchiModules()`** concatenates `databaseModule` + **`sharedKoinArchiModules`**.

**In app** (`PokeManiacApplication.kt`):
```kotlin
startKoin {
    androidContext(this@PokeManiacApplication)
    modules(appCoreArchiModules())
    modules(myFeatureModule)
}
```

### Injection in ViewModel
```kotlin
class MyFeatureViewModel(
    private val myRepository: MyRepository,  // Resolved from domain
    private val navigator: MyNavigator,      // Resolved from coreui
    private val tracking: TrackingRepository  // Resolved from tracking
) : ViewModel()
```

