## Tracking & Analytics

Features can log events via `TrackingRepository`:

```kotlin
class MyFeatureViewModel(
    ...
    private val tracking: TrackingRepository
) {
    fun onItemClicked(itemId: String) {
        tracking.logEvent("item_clicked", mapOf("id" to itemId))
    }
}
```

Currently mocked locally; can be connected to Firebase, Segment, etc.

