### Add Database Table
→ Create `*Base` entity (Room)
→ Create `*Dao` interface
→ Create `*DataStore` interface + `*DataStoreImpl`
→ Register in `databaseModule`

### Add Screen Route Navigation
→ Define `@Serializable data class Route` in feature
→ Add to `Routes` sealed class
→ Use `composable<Route> { ... }`
→ Navigate: `navController.navigate(Route(...))`

### Add Unit Test
→ Extend `ViewModel` test with `UnconfinedTestDispatcher`
→ Mock dependencies with `mockk<Interface>()`
→ Use `viewModel.stateFlow.test { ... }` (Turbine)
→ Follow Given/When/Then pattern

