## Troubleshooting

### ViewModel not receiving data
1. Check `ViewModel.start()` is called in `Screen` lifecycle
2. Verify Flow is emitting in repository
3. Confirm `collectAsState()` is active

### Feature module not found
1. Check `settings.gradle.kts` includes module
2. Check `app/build.gradle.kts` has implementation dependency
3. Run Gradle sync

### Koin injection fails
1. Check module is registered in `PokeManiacApplication.kt`
2. Verify interface/implementation are declared in right module
3. Check constructor parameter types match bindings

### Compose preview not showing
1. Add `@Preview` annotation before `@Composable`
2. Wrap in `PokeManiacTheme { ... }`
3. Check imports are correct

